questions.text: You're at a party and someone spills a drink on you. Your first reaction is to:

choices.text: Laugh it off and join the dance floor with your new 'design'.
Analyze whether it was an accident or intentional.
Comfort the person, saying it's okay even if you're upset.

choices.text: Immediately think of all the fun things you could do with the money.
Plan a systematic approach to find the owner using the ID.
Feel deeply for the person who lost it and go out of your way to return it.
